CHIC Landscape Analysis Exploratory Analysis

Danica Shipley

26 October, 2020

Methodology

Individual Survey Respondents

Community Survey Respondents Overall, 190 people participated in CHICs community survey; 117 of whom identified as Women of Color. The survey ran from August 24, 2020 to September 27, 2020 and was administered in both English and Spanish.
